net.sf.sprockets.content

Class MutableSql

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.sprockets.content.DbContentProvider.Sql
      • net.sf.sprockets.content.MutableSql

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
@NotThreadSafe
public class MutableSql
extends DbContentProvider.Sql
    Modifiable implementation of Sql.

    Use constructor to create new modifiable instances. You may even extend this class to add some convenience methods, however most of the methods in this class are final to preserve safety and predictable invariants.

    MutableSql is not thread safe

    See Also:
    ImmutableSql
